{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Video: Narrator: An event seen from one point of view"},{"time":3000,"text":"gives one impression."},{"time":8000,"text":"Seen from another point of view, it gives quite a different impression."},{"time":13000,"text":"But it's only when you get the whole picture you can fully understand"},{"time":17000,"text":"what's going on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20000,"text":"Sasha Vucinic: It's a great clip, isn't it?"},{"time":23000,"text":"And I found that in 29 seconds, it tells more about"},{"time":28000,"text":"the power of, and importance of, independent media"},{"time":31000,"text":"than I could say in an hour."},{"time":34000,"text":"So I thought that it will be good to start with it."},{"time":38000,"text":"And also start with a little bit of statistics."},{"time":41000,"text":"According to relevant researchers, 83 percent of the population of this planet"},{"time":47000,"text":"lives in the societies without independent press."},{"time":52000,"text":"Think about that number: 83 percent of the population on the whole planet"},{"time":57000,"text":"does not really know what is going on in their countries."},{"time":61000,"text":"The information they get gets filtered through somebody"},{"time":65000,"text":"who either twists that information, or colors that information,"},{"time":69000,"text":"does something with it."},{"time":70000,"text":"So they're deprived of understanding their reality."},{"time":75000,"text":"That is just to understand how big and important this problem is."},{"time":81000,"text":"Now those of you who are lucky enough to live in those societies"},{"time":88000,"text":"that represent 17 percent, I think should enjoy it until it lasts."},{"time":94000,"text":"You know, Sunday morning, you flick the paper, get your cappuccino."},{"time":98000,"text":"Enjoy it while it lasts."},{"time":99000,"text":"Because as we heard yesterday, countries can lose stars from their flags,"},{"time":106000,"text":"but they can also lose press freedom,"},{"time":109000,"text":"as I guess Americans among us can tell us more about."},{"time":114000,"text":"But that's totally another and separate topic."},{"time":117000,"text":"So I can go back to my story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121000,"text":"My story starts -- the story I want to share -- starts in 1991."},{"time":126000,"text":"At that time I was running B92, the only independent,"},{"time":130000,"text":"for that matter the only electronic media, in the country."},{"time":133000,"text":"And I guess we were sharing -- we had that regular life of the only"},{"time":138000,"text":"independent media in the country, operating in hostile environment,"},{"time":144000,"text":"where government really wants to make your life miserable."},{"time":148000,"text":"And there are different ways."},{"time":149000,"text":"Yeah, it was the usual cocktail:"},{"time":150000,"text":"a little bit of threats, a little bit of friendly advice,"},{"time":153000,"text":"a little bit of financial police, a little bit of text control,"},{"time":157000,"text":"so you always have somebody who never leaves your office."},{"time":161000,"text":"But what they really do, which is very powerful,"},{"time":166000,"text":"and that is what governments in the late '90s started doing"},{"time":170000,"text":"if they don't like independent media companies --"},{"time":172000,"text":"you know, they threaten your advertisers."},{"time":174000,"text":"Once they threaten your advertisers, market forces are actually,"},{"time":179000,"text":"you know, destroyed, and the advertisers do not want to come --"},{"time":184000,"text":"no matter how much does it make sense for them --"},{"time":187000,"text":"do not want to come and advertise."},{"time":189000,"text":"And you have a problem making ends meet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"At that time at the beginning of the '90s, we had that problem,"},{"time":197000,"text":"which was, you know, survival below one side,"},{"time":199000,"text":"but what was really painful for me was,"},{"time":203000,"text":"remember, the beginning of the '90s, Yugoslavia is falling apart."},{"time":206000,"text":"We were sitting over there with a country in a downfall,"},{"time":209000,"text":"in a slow-motion downfall."},{"time":213000,"text":"And we all had all of that on tapes."},{"time":216000,"text":"We had the ability to understand what was going on."},{"time":219000,"text":"We were actually recording history."},{"time":221000,"text":"The problem was that we had to re-tape that history a week later;"},{"time":226000,"text":"because if we did not, we could not afford enough tapes"},{"time":230000,"text":"to keep archives of that history."},{"time":233000,"text":"So if I gave you that picture, I don't want to go too long on that."},{"time":238000,"text":"In that context a gentleman came to my office at that time."},{"time":242000,"text":"It was still 1991."},{"time":243000,"text":"He was running a media systems organization"},{"time":246000,"text":"which is still in business, the gentleman is still in business."},{"time":249000,"text":"And what did I know at that time about media systems?"},{"time":252000,"text":"I would think media systems were organizations,"},{"time":255000,"text":"which means they should help you."},{"time":259000,"text":"So I prepared two plans for that meeting, two strategic plans:"},{"time":262000,"text":"the small one and the big one."},{"time":264000,"text":"The small one was, I just wanted him"},{"time":266000,"text":"to help us get those damn tapes,"},{"time":268000,"text":"so we can keep that archive for the next 50 years."},{"time":272000,"text":"The big plan was to ask him for a 1,000,000-dollar loan."},{"time":277000,"text":"Because I thought, I still maintain,"},{"time":280000,"text":"that serious and independent media companies are great business."},{"time":284000,"text":"And I thought that B92 will survive and be a great company"},{"time":288000,"text":"once Milosevic is gone, which turned out to be true."},{"time":291000,"text":"It's now probably either the biggest or the second biggest"},{"time":294000,"text":"media company in the country."},{"time":296000,"text":"And I thought that the only thing that we needed at that time"},{"time":299000,"text":"was 1,000,000-dollar loan to take us through those hard times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303000,"text":"To make a long story short, the gentleman comes into the office,"},{"time":307000,"text":"great suit and tie."},{"time":311000,"text":"I gave him what I thought was a brilliant explanation"},{"time":315000,"text":"of the political situation and explained how hard and difficult"},{"time":320000,"text":"the war will be."},{"time":322000,"text":"Actually, I underestimated the atrocities, I have to admit."},{"time":325000,"text":"Anyway, after that whole, big, long explanation,"},{"time":328000,"text":"the only question he had for me -- and this is not a joke --"},{"time":333000,"text":"is, are we paying royalties after we broadcast music"},{"time":337000,"text":"of Michael Jackson?"},{"time":341000,"text":"That was really the only question he had."},{"time":343000,"text":"He left, and I remember being actually very angry at myself"},{"time":350000,"text":"because I thought there must be an institution in the world"},{"time":354000,"text":"that is providing loans to media companies."},{"time":357000,"text":"It's so obvious, straight in your face,"},{"time":360000,"text":"and somebody must have thought of it."},{"time":361000,"text":"Somebody must have started something like that."},{"time":364000,"text":"And I thought, I'm just dumb and I cannot find it."},{"time":368000,"text":"You know, in my defense, there was no Google at that time;"},{"time":370000,"text":"you could not just Google in '91."},{"time":373000,"text":"So I thought that that's actually my problem."},{"time":377000,"text":"Now we go from here, fast forward to 1995."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381000,"text":"I have -- I left the country, I have a meeting with George Soros,"},{"time":387000,"text":"trying for the third time to convince him that"},{"time":393000,"text":"his foundation should invest in something that should"},{"time":396000,"text":"operate like a media bank."},{"time":400000,"text":"And basically what I was saying is very simple."},{"time":403000,"text":"You know, forget about charity; it doesn't work."},{"time":404000,"text":"Forget about handouts; 20,000 dollars do not help anybody."},{"time":409000,"text":"What you should do is you should treat media companies as a business."},{"time":413000,"text":"It's business anywhere."},{"time":415000,"text":"Media business, or any other business, it needs to be capitalized."},{"time":418000,"text":"And what these guys need, actually, is access to capital."},{"time":423000,"text":"So third meeting, arguments are pretty well exercised."},{"time":428000,"text":"At the end of the meeting he says,"},{"time":430000,"text":"look, it is not going to work; you will never see your money back;"},{"time":434000,"text":"but my foundations will put 500,000 dollars so you can test the idea."},{"time":439000,"text":"See that it will not work."},{"time":444000,"text":"He said, I'll give you a rope to hang yourself."},{"time":446000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":448000,"text":"I knew two things after that meeting."},{"time":451000,"text":"First, under no circumstances I want to hang myself."},{"time":455000,"text":"And second, that I have no idea how to make it work."},{"time":461000,"text":"You see, at the level of a concept, it was a great concept."},{"time":465000,"text":"But it's one thing to have a concept;"},{"time":467000,"text":"it's a totally separate thing to actually make it work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":470000,"text":"So I had absolutely no idea how that could actually work."},{"time":474000,"text":"Had the wrong idea; I thought that we can be a bank."},{"time":477000,"text":"You see banks -- I don't know if there are any bankers over here;"},{"time":480000,"text":"I apologize in advance -- but it's the best job in the world."},{"time":484000,"text":"You know, you find somebody who is respectable"},{"time":487000,"text":"and has a lot of money."},{"time":488000,"text":"You give them more money; they repay you that over a time."},{"time":493000,"text":"You collect interest and do nothing in between."},{"time":495000,"text":"So I thought, why don't we get into that business?"},{"time":497000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":499000,"text":"So here we are having our first client, brilliant."},{"time":505000,"text":"First independent newspaper in Slovakia."},{"time":507000,"text":"The government cutting them off"},{"time":508000,"text":"from all the printing facilities in Bratislava."},{"time":511000,"text":"So here's the daily newspaper"},{"time":512000,"text":"that has to be printed 400 kilometers away from the capital."},{"time":516000,"text":"It's a daily newspaper with a deadline of 4 p.m."},{"time":520000,"text":"That means that they have no sports;"},{"time":522000,"text":"they have no latest news; circulation goes down."},{"time":525000,"text":"It's a kind of very nice, sophisticated way"},{"time":528000,"text":"how to economically strangle a daily newspaper."},{"time":532000,"text":"They come to us with a request for a loan."},{"time":534000,"text":"They want to -- the only way for them to survive"},{"time":536000,"text":"is to get a printing press."},{"time":538000,"text":"And we said, that's fine; let's meet;"},{"time":541000,"text":"you'll bring us your business plan, which eventually they did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":545000,"text":"We start the meeting."},{"time":547000,"text":"I get these two pieces of paper, not like this, A4 format,"},{"time":551000,"text":"so it's much bigger."},{"time":553000,"text":"A lot of numbers there. A lot of numbers."},{"time":556000,"text":"But however you put it, you know, the numbers"},{"time":558000,"text":"do not make any sense."},{"time":560000,"text":"And that's the best they could do."},{"time":562000,"text":"We were the best that they could do."},{"time":563000,"text":"So that is how we understood what our method is."},{"time":565000,"text":"It's not a bank. We had to actually"},{"time":568000,"text":"go into these companies and earn our return"},{"time":572000,"text":"by fixing them -- by establishing management systems,"},{"time":575000,"text":"by providing all that knowledge, how do you run a business"},{"time":577000,"text":"on one side -- while they all know how to run, how to create content."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583000,"text":"Just quickly on the results."},{"time":589000,"text":"Over these 10 years, 40 million dollars in affordable financing,"},{"time":595000,"text":"average interest rate five percent to six percent."},{"time":598000,"text":"Lately we are going wild, charging seven percent from time to time."},{"time":604000,"text":"We do it in 17 countries of the developing world."},{"time":608000,"text":"And here is the most stunning number."},{"time":611000,"text":"Return rate -- the one that Soros was so worried about -- 97 percent."},{"time":617000,"text":"97 percent of all the scheduled repayments came back to us on time."},{"time":622000,"text":"What do we typically finance?"},{"time":623000,"text":"We finance anything that a media company would need,"},{"time":626000,"text":"from printing presses to transmitters."},{"time":631000,"text":"What is most important is we do it"},{"time":636000,"text":"either in form of loans, equities, lease --"},{"time":639000,"text":"whatever is appropriate for, you know, supporting anybody."},{"time":642000,"text":"But what is most important here is, who do we finance?"},{"time":647000,"text":"We believe that in the last 10 years companies"},{"time":649000,"text":"that we've financed are actually the best media companies"},{"time":653000,"text":"in the developing world."},{"time":655000,"text":"That is a \"Who is Who\" list."},{"time":657000,"text":"And I could spend hours talking about them,"},{"time":662000,"text":"because they're all kind of heroes."},{"time":663000,"text":"And I can, but I'll give you just, maybe one,"},{"time":666000,"text":"and depending on time I may give you two examples"},{"time":669000,"text":"who we work with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":670000,"text":"You see we started working in Eastern and Central Europe,"},{"time":672000,"text":"and moved to Russia."},{"time":674000,"text":"Our first loan in Russia was in Chelyabinsk."},{"time":677000,"text":"I'll bet half of you have never heard of that place."},{"time":680000,"text":"In the south of Russia there's a guy called"},{"time":683000,"text":"Boris Nikolayevich Kirshin, who is running"},{"time":685000,"text":"an independent newspaper there."},{"time":687000,"text":"The city was closed until early '90s"},{"time":689000,"text":"because, of all things, they were producing glass for Tupolev planes."},{"time":696000,"text":"Anyway, he's running independent newspaper there."},{"time":700000,"text":"After two years working with us, he becomes"},{"time":702000,"text":"the most respected newspaper in that small place."},{"time":708000,"text":"Governor comes to him one day,"},{"time":710000,"text":"actually invites him to come to his office."},{"time":712000,"text":"He goes and sees the governor. The governor says,"},{"time":715000,"text":"Boris Nikolayevich, I understand you are doing a great job,"},{"time":717000,"text":"and you are the most respected newspaper in our district."},{"time":723000,"text":"And I want to offer you a deal."},{"time":727000,"text":"Can you please give me your newspaper for the next nine months,"},{"time":730000,"text":"because I have elections --"},{"time":732000,"text":"there are elections coming up in nine months."},{"time":735000,"text":"I will not run, but it's very important for me"},{"time":738000,"text":"who is going to succeed me."},{"time":740000,"text":"So give me the paper for nine months. I'll give it back to you."},{"time":742000,"text":"I have no interest in being in media business."},{"time":745000,"text":"How much would that cost?"},{"time":748000,"text":"Boris Nikolayevich says, \"It's not for sale.\""},{"time":750000,"text":"The governor says, \"We will close you.\""},{"time":753000,"text":"Boris Nikolayevich says, \"No, you cannot do it.\""},{"time":755000,"text":"Six months later the newspaper was closed."},{"time":759000,"text":"Luckily, we had enough time to help Boris Nikolayevich"},{"time":762000,"text":"take all the assets out of that company and bring him into a new one,"},{"time":766000,"text":"to get all the subscription lists, rehire staff."},{"time":770000,"text":"So what the governor got was an empty shell."},{"time":773000,"text":"But that is what happens if you're in business of independent media,"},{"time":777000,"text":"and if you are a banker for independent media."},{"time":781000,"text":"So it sounds like a great story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787000,"text":"Somewhere down the road we opened a media management center."},{"time":791000,"text":"We started our media lab, sounds like a real great story."},{"time":794000,"text":"But there is a second angle to that."},{"time":797000,"text":"The second angle, like in this clip."},{"time":799000,"text":"If you take the camera above, you start thinking"},{"time":801000,"text":"about these numbers again."},{"time":802000,"text":"40 million dollars over 10 years spread over 17 countries."},{"time":809000,"text":"That is not too much, is it?"},{"time":811000,"text":"It's actually just a drop in the sea."},{"time":813000,"text":"Because when you think about the importance,"},{"time":815000,"text":"some of the issues that we were talking about last night --"},{"time":818000,"text":"this last session we had about Africa and his"},{"time":820000,"text":"hypothetical 50 billion dollars destined for Africa."},{"time":825000,"text":"All of those, not all, half of those problems mentioned last night --"},{"time":831000,"text":"government accountability, corruption, how do you fight corruption,"},{"time":836000,"text":"giving voice to unheard, to poor --"},{"time":839000,"text":"it's why independent media is in business."},{"time":843000,"text":"And it's why it was invented."},{"time":845000,"text":"So from that perspective, what we did is just really"},{"time":848000,"text":"one drop in the sea of that need that we can identify."},{"time":855000,"text":"Now ours is just one story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":858000,"text":"I'm sure that in this room there are, like, 15 other wonderful stories"},{"time":861000,"text":"of nonprofits doing spectacular work."},{"time":864000,"text":"Here is where the problem is,"},{"time":867000,"text":"and I'll explain to you as well as I can what the problem is."},{"time":873000,"text":"And it's called fundraising."},{"time":875000,"text":"Imagine that this third of this room is filled"},{"time":879000,"text":"with people who represent different foundations."},{"time":882000,"text":"Imagine two thirds over here running excellent organizations,"},{"time":887000,"text":"doing very important work."},{"time":890000,"text":"Now imagine that every second person over here"},{"time":892000,"text":"is deaf, does not hear, and switch the lights off."},{"time":897000,"text":"Now that is how difficult it is to match people"},{"time":899000,"text":"from this side of the room"},{"time":901000,"text":"with people of that side of the room."},{"time":904000,"text":"So we thought that some kind of a big idea is needed"},{"time":909000,"text":"to reform, to totally rethink fundraising."},{"time":914000,"text":"You know, instead of people running in this dark,"},{"time":916000,"text":"trying to find their own match, who will be willing,"},{"time":919000,"text":"who has the same goals."},{"time":921000,"text":"Instead of all of that we thought there is --"},{"time":924000,"text":"something new needs to be invented."},{"time":927000,"text":"And we came up with this idea of issuing bonds,"},{"time":930000,"text":"press freedom bonds."},{"time":931000,"text":"If there are investors willing to finance"},{"time":938000,"text":"U.S. government budget deficit,"},{"time":940000,"text":"why wouldn't we find investors willing to finance"},{"time":943000,"text":"press freedom deficit?"},{"time":946000,"text":"We've decided to do it this fall; we will issue them,"},{"time":948000,"text":"probably in denominations of 1,000 dollars."},{"time":951000,"text":"I don't want to advertise them too much; that's not the point."},{"time":953000,"text":"But the point is, if we ever survive to actually issue them,"},{"time":957000,"text":"find enough investors that this can be considered a success,"},{"time":961000,"text":"there's nothing stopping the next organization"},{"time":964000,"text":"to start to issue bonds next spring."},{"time":969000,"text":"And those can be environmental bonds."},{"time":971000,"text":"And then two weeks later, Iqbal Quadir can issue his"},{"time":976000,"text":"electricity in Bangladesh bonds."},{"time":979000,"text":"And before you know it, any social cause"},{"time":982000,"text":"can be actually financed in this way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":985000,"text":"Now we do daydreaming in 11:30 with 55 seconds left."},{"time":990000,"text":"But let's take the idea further."},{"time":992000,"text":"You do it, you start it in the States, because it's,"},{"time":995000,"text":"you know, concepts are very, very close to American minds."},{"time":998000,"text":"But you can actually bring it to Europe, too."},{"time":1000000,"text":"You can bring it to Asia."},{"time":1002000,"text":"You can, once you have all of those different points,"},{"time":1006000,"text":"you can make it easy for investors."},{"time":1008000,"text":"Put all of those bonds at one place"},{"time":1010000,"text":"and they sit down and click."},{"time":1012000,"text":"Once you have more than 10 of them"},{"time":1014000,"text":"you have to develop some kind of a matrix."},{"time":1017000,"text":"What do investors get?"},{"time":1018000,"text":"On one side financial, on the other side social."},{"time":1021000,"text":"So that brings the idea of some kind of rating agency,"},{"time":1027000,"text":"Morningstar type."},{"time":1029000,"text":"It says, you know, social impact over here is spectacular, five stars."},{"time":1033000,"text":"Financial, they give you one percent, only one star."},{"time":1037000,"text":"Now take it to the last step."},{"time":1041000,"text":"Once you have all of that put together,"},{"time":1043000,"text":"there's not one reason why you couldn't actually have"},{"time":1048000,"text":"a marketplace for all of that,"},{"time":1050000,"text":"where you cannot dispose of all of those bonds in a pretty quick way."},{"time":1055000,"text":"And in that way you organize the financing"},{"time":1058000,"text":"so there are no dark rooms, no blind people"},{"time":1060000,"text":"running around to find each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1062000,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}